{"id": "1194261032458276925", "channel_id": "1193425558286114826", "type": 0, "author_id": "977101500675403796", "author_name": "rsiane_yomi", "author_bot": false, "content": "我有開一個帖了 具體講過一次但有人推薦我可以來這問才來的🥹", "timestamp": "2024-01-09T12:46:58.435000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1193425558286114826", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "採訪校貓區", "forum_channel_id": "1180845276823564288", "thread_tags": ["1181168158678204497"]}
{"id": "1194261171247788084", "channel_id": "1193425558286114826", "type": 0, "author_id": "546511962977337344", "author_name": "07_li", "author_bot": false, "content": "如果是第三方支付那就是從第三方那邊申請退款，但如果是從代理商或是官方直儲的或就要詢問代理商。", "timestamp": "2024-01-09T12:47:31.525000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1193425558286114826", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "採訪校貓區", "forum_channel_id": "1180845276823564288", "thread_tags": ["1181168158678204497"]}
